Simple site using sinatra (https://github.com/sinatra/sinatra) for http://rubyftw.org

$ rake -T
rake setup:bundler  # Checks bundle and installs anything missing
rake site:hack      # Start a server on port 3601

Clone the project and type rake to start a web server on port 3601 and open your
browser up to http://localhost:3601 then hack away at the files and watch the
evolution of the site from your browser. 

Watch this repository to be added to the list of current members (will be
reflected on the next update to the site)
